<h1 class="journal-title">{{ title }}</h1>

<div class="journal-introduction" {{ site.animationDelay }}>
	<p>
		Writing is a passion for me. Iâ€™ve written a huge collection of essays about
		<a href="https://www.kogakure.de/" {{ site.external | safe }}>Ninja&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Ninjutsu</a>
		that I later converted into a book. The online publishing
		platform <cite>Medium</cite> selected <a href="/attention/">one of my essays</a> as a
